        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><hr /><p>You use some of your host's energy to trigger immense growth in your mycelium network, growing a protective layer of tough, oozy fungus. For 1 minute, you gain a +2 status bonus to AC and resistance 10 to physical damage, and are @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1}. If you gain Hit Points or temporary Hit Points while this ability is active, until the end of your next turn, you deal an additional @Damage[2d6[poison]] damage with all your unarmed melee Strikes.</p>"
